            </ul>
            <p>The biggest highlight? <span class="font-weight-700"> India’s first automatic CNG hatchback.</span> With <span class="font-weight-700">direct CNG start, single advanced ECU, and twin-cylinder layout,</span> Tata ensures CNG buyers get the same comfort and performance as petrol. </p>

